---
title: Indian-Style Chickpea Coconut Curry Served with Basmati Rice & Topped with Yogurt
description: Curries are one of those meals that warms your heart and your belly—for Asian Heritage Month, try this vegetarian version that’s no exception! Chickpeas, onion, and bell pepper get a super savory treatment in a coconut-based curry sauce. Serve it over rice, add a dollop of yogurt and a sprinkle of cilantro, and you have yourself one soul-satisfying meal.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/661d670db4db7806c6d9defc-713df8e4.jpeg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipecards/card/661d670db4db7806c6d9defc-en-US.pdf
cuisine: Indian
author: Michelle Doll Olson
source: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipes/indian-style-chickpea-coconut-curry-661d670db4db7806c6d9defc
servings: 2
course: main course
nutrition:
  calories: 820 kcal
  fat: 37 g
